article_title: New Data Shows Large Insurer Losses On Obamacare Plans

article_metadata.author: The Apothecary

og.description: In this column, I use the recently released risk corridor information and other data sources to estimate overall insurer losses on Obamacare plans in 2014. The magnitude of the estimated losses is further indication that younger and healthier people have not signed up for coverage to the degree that insurers and the Obama administration anticipated.
